      <Content>It is possible to interpret κληρονόμος in {S:05900200500034} (and particularly in {S:05600300700012}) as identifying essentially a future experiencer, but with the additional components of the experience being valuable and not having been worked for. In this respect κληρονόμος overlaps between Subdomain I, Receive, in Domain 57 Possess, Transfer, Exchange, and Domain 90 Case.</Content>
